{"tid":184478,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【執法】傳大摩、瑞銀、美銀美林被查　疑涉天合化工造假上市","createTime":"2017-04-02T23:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T00:01:50.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c17d4e0b85d650e5a8d72edc1081ec7ff7f49e2","tid":184478,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T23:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/03/073154_f8a39d5aad67aafa933c13008231e7bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F03%2F073154_f8a39d5aad67aafa933c13008231e7bf.jpg&h=5c2e4449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述消息指，證監會向摩根士丹利、瑞銀、美銀美林調查，疑涉天合化工（1619）涉造假上市一事，該股停牌至今已2年多。<br />\n<br />\n天合化工挾內地最大潤滑油添加生產商之名，2014年來港上市，集資50.7億元，上市保薦人及承銷團粒粒皆星，除上述三行，尚有高盛、中銀國際、工銀國際等。<br />\n<br />\n但天合化工上市兩個月就被沽空機構Anonymous Analytics攻擊，指其誇大收入及盈利，目標價0元，更指瑞銀曾聘用天合化工董事長魏奇之女魏嬌，涉利益衝突。當年3名涉事賓架已被瑞銀內部調查及要求休假。<br />\n<br />\n天合化工被狙擊前股價2.31元，及後跌至1.10元，更因為未能如期刊發2014、15、16年全年業績及年報，停牌至今。<br />\n<br />\n去年底渣打、瑞銀於業績自爆，被證監會調查2009年保薦人失當事宜，料與中國森林（930，已除牌）造假上市案有關。證監會去年上任的法規執行部董事魏建新改組執法部門，主力調查具影響力的案件，亦設專責小組調查保薦人失職、創業板股份等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56514458&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56514458%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170402&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=07744fdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56514458%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170402&h=91f9333f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56514458&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170402</a>"},{"pid":"6c8eb99c2fe0fa4961daa138c16ed2d7b89c7dad","tid":184478,"uid":66987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:01:50.000Z","msg":"有李小加保住，唔會有事"}]}